    "summary": "Steadily exposes two partner REST APIs on api.steadily.com (Partner API and Rater Quotes API) that use Steadily-issued API keys—plus bearer tokens for quoting endpoints in the Rater API—and a public no-auth MCP server at https://mcp.steadily.com/mcp per the catalog.",
